+## OneLuaPro Integration
+
+This VSCode extension is specifically tailored for seamless integration with the [OneLuaPro](https://github.com/OneLuaPro) ecosystem. While based on the excellent work of [sumneko](https://github.com/LuaLS) and the whole LuaLS team, this version features several key adjustments:
+- **Optimized for OneLuaPro**: Pre-configured to work out-of-the-box with OneLuaPro environments.
+- **Lua 5.5 Support**: Built with Lua 5.5 as the default standard for modern development.
+- **Enhanced Stability**: Features statically linked runtime libraries to ensure a predictable development experience.
+
+
 ## Features
 
 - ⚙️ Supports `Lua 5.5`, `Lua 5.4`, `Lua 5.3`, `Lua 5.2`, `Lua 5.1`, and `LuaJIT`
